quran[83]{c,v,t}:
  36,1,“Yâ-Sîn
  36,2,“Ndikulumbira Qur’an (iyi yomwe yakonzedwa mwaluso) yodzazidwa ndi mawu anzeru
  36,3,"“Ndithu iwe (Muhammad {s.a.w}) ndimmodzi wa atumiki (amene Allah adawatuma kwa anthu kuti akawasonyeze chiongoko)"
  36,4,“(Uli) panjira yolunjika
  36,5,“(Qur’an iyi) nchivumbulutso cha Mwini Mphamvu zoposa; (palibe chokanika kwa Iye) Wachisoni chosatha
  36,6,“Kuti uwachenjeze anthu omwe makolo awo sadachenjezedwe; choncho iwo ngoiwala (zomwe zili zofunika kuchitira Allah ndi kudzichitira okha pamodzi ndi anthu ena)
  36,7,“Ndithu mawu (onena za chilango) atsimikizika pa ambiri a iwo; poti iwo sakhulupirira
  36,8,"“Ndithu Ife taika magoli m’makosi mwawo ofika kuzibwano, kotero kuti mitu yawo yayang’ana mmwamba; (siingathe kutembenuka ndi kuyang’ana)"
  36,9,"“Ndipo tawaikira chotsekereza patsogolo pawo ndi chotsekereza pambuyo pawo, ndipo (maso awo) tawaphimba, tero iwo saona (zapatsogolo ndi pambuyo pawo)"
  36,10,"“Ndipo kwa iwo nchimodzimodzi, uwachenjeze ngakhale usawachenjeze sangakhulupirire"
  36,11,“Ndithu kuchenjeza kwako kupindulira amene watsatira Qur’an ndi kumuopa (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri ngakhale sakumuona. Wotere muuze nkhani yabwino ya chikhululuko (chochokera kwa Allah pa machimo ake) ndi malipiro aulemu
  36,12,"“Ndithu Ife tidzaukitsa akufa, ndipo tikulemba zimene atsogoza (m’dziko lapansi m’zochita zawo) ndi zomwe amasiya pambuyo (atafa, zonkerankera mtsogolo), ndipo chinthu chilichonse tachilemba m’kaundula wopenyeka (wofotokoza chilichonse)"
  36,13,“Ndipo pereka kwa iwo (iwe Mneneri) fanizo la (nkhani ya) eni mudzi pamene atumiki (a Allah) adaudzera mudziwo (kuti akaaongole eni mudziwo)
  36,14,"“Pamene tidatumiza atumiki awiri kwa iwo adawatsutsa; ndipo tidawalimbitsa iwo (awiriwo) potumiza wachitatu. (Atumiki atatuwo) adati: “Ife tatumidwa kwa inu.”"
  36,15,"“(Eni mudzi) adati: “Inu ndi anthu ngati ife; (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri sadavumbulutse chilichonse (kwa munthu); inu simuli kanthu koma mukunena bodza.”"
  36,16,"“(Atumiki) adati: “Mbuye wathu (Amene watituma kwa inu) akudziwa kuti ife ndi otumidwadi kwa inu.”"
  36,17,"““Ndipo palibe china pa ife, koma kufikitsa mwachimvekere (uthenga wa Allah).”"
  36,18,"“(Eni mudzi) adati: “Ife tapeza tsoka chifukwa cha inu; ngati simusiya (ulaliki wanuwo wofuna kutichotsa ku chipembedzo chathu) tikugendani ndi miyala; ndipo kuchokera kwa ife chikukhudzani chilango chowawa.”"
  36,19,"“(Atumiki) adati: “Tsoka lanu lili ndi inu (chifukwa cha kukana kwanu ndi kupitiriza kupembedza mafano). Kodi mukakumbutsidwa (ndi mawu omwe m’kati mwake muli mtendere wanu mukuti takudzetserani masoka; ndi kumatiopseza ndi chilango chowawa)? Koma inu ndi anthu olumpha malire.”"
  36,20,"“Kenako munthu adadza akuthamanga kuchokera ku malekezero a mzindawo (ndipo) adati: “E inu anthu anga! Atsateni atumikiwa.”"
  36,21,"““Atsateni omwe sakupemphani malipiro (pa kukulangizani kwawo), ndipo iwo ngoongoka.”"
  36,22,““Kodi nchiyani chingandiletse ine kupembedza Yemwe adandilenga? Ndipo kwa Iye ndi komwe inu nonse mudzabwerera.”
  36,23,““Kodi ndidzipangire milungu kusiya Iye (Allah)? Chipulumutso chawo sichingandipindulire chilichonse ngati (Allah) Wachifundo Chambiri atafuna kundichitira zoipa; ndipo siingandipulumutse.”
  36,24,““Ndithu ine ngati nditatero ndiye kuti ndili mchisokero choonekera poyera”
  36,25,““Ndithu ine ndakhulupirira Mbuye wanu choncho ndimvereni.”
  36,26,"“Kudanenedwa (kwa iye): “Lowa m’Munda wamtendere.” Iye adati: “Ha! Anthu anga akadadziwa!”"
  36,27,““Momwe Mbuye wanga wandikhululukira ndikundichita kukhala mmodzi wa opatsidwa ulemu (akadakhulupirira).”
  36,28,"“Ndipo anthu ake sitidawatsitsire ankhondo ochokera kumwamba pambuyo pake (kuti awaononge). Ndipo pachizolowezi chathu sititsitsa (ankhondo kumwamba tikafuna kuononga, koma Mngelo mmodzi amakwanira)"
  36,29,"“(Kuonongeka kwawo) kudali mkuwe umodzi, ndipo nthawi yomweyo adali akufa (izi zidachitika pamene mngelo Gabuliyele adawakuwira mkuwe wamphamvu)"
  36,30,“Ha! Nzodandaulitsa kwa akapolo! Palibe pamene mtumiki adawadzera popanda kumchitira chipongwe (ndi kukana kumtsata)
  36,31,“Kodi sadalingalire za mibadwo yambirimbiri imene tidaiononga patsogolo pawo? Ndipo iwo sangabwelerenso kwa iwo
  36,32,“Ndipo zolengedwa zonse zidzaonekera kwa Ife
  36,33,"“Ndipo chisonyezo chawo ndi nthaka yakufa; timaiukitsa (ndi madzi) ndi kutulutsa m’menemo njere, zomwe zina mwa izo amadya"
  36,34,“Ndipo tapanga m’menemo minda ya kanjedza ndi mphesa; ndipo tatulutsa m’menemo akasupe
  36,35,“Kuti azidya zipatso zake pomwe sizidapangidwe ndi manja awo. Kodi bwanji sathokoza (Allah)
  36,36,"“Alemekezeke (Allah), Amene adalenga zinthu zonse, chachimuna ndi chachikazi, kuchokera m’zimene nthaka ikutulutsa, ndi iwo omwe ndi zina zimene (anthu) sakudziwa"
  36,37,"“Ndiponso chisonyezo chawo ndiusiku. M’menemo timachotsamo usana (womwe umabisa usiku), ndipo (anthu) amangozindikira ali mu mdima"
  36,38,"“۞ Ndipo dzuwa; limayenda m’njira ndi m’nthawi yake imene idakonzedwa kwa ilo. Chikonzero chimenecho ncha (Allah) Wamphamvu zoposa, Wodziwa kwambiri"
  36,39,"“Ndiponso mwezi; tidaukonzera malo oimirapo mpaka kukafika pomwe umabwerera ndi kukhala wochepa ndi wokhota monga nthambi ya mtengo wa kanjedza, youma komanso yokhota"
  36,40,"“Nkosatheka kwa dzuwa kukumana ndi mwezi (njira yake); nawonso usiku sungathe kupambana usana (pakudza nthawi yausana isadathe, koma zimasinthana). Ndipo chilichonse mwa izo chimasambira m’njira yake (imene Allah adachikonzera)"
  36,41,“Ndiponso pali chisonyezo kwa iwo (chosonyeza madalitso Athu pa iwo). Ndithu tidaukweza mtundu wawo mchombo chodzazidwa (ndi zonse zamoyo)
  36,42,“Ndipo tidawapangira chonga icho chomwe akuchikwera
  36,43,"“Ndipo ngati titafuna tikhoza kuwamiza m’madzi, ndipo sangapezeke wowathandiza, ndiponso sangapulumutsidwe"
  36,44,“Koma (sitikuwamiza) chifukwa cha chifundo Chathu pa iwo ndi kuti asangalale kufikira nthawi yawo (yofera)
  36,45,"“Ndipo kukanenedwa kwa iwo: “Opani zomwe ziri patsogolo panu ndi zomwe ziri pambuyo panu kuti muchitiridwe chifundo.” (Iwo akunyoza malangizowo)"
  36,46,“Ndipo palibe chisonyezo chilichonse mwa zisonyezo za Mbuye wawo (zosonyeza umodzi Wake ndi kukhoza Kwake) chomwe chidawadzera popanda kuchinyoza (ndi kuchikana)
  36,47,"“Ndipo kukanenedwa kwa iwo: “Patsani (amphawi) zimene Allah wakupatsani.” Osakhulupirira amanena kwa okhulupirira: “Kodi tidyetse yemwe Allah akadafuna akadamdyetsa; (titsutsane ndi cholinga cha Allah)? Ndithu inu simuli kanthu koma muli m’kusokera koonekeratu.”"
  36,48,"“Ndipo akunena (mwachipongwe kwa okhulupirira): “Kodi lonjezo ili (lakudza kwa chiweruziro), lidzachitika liti, ngati mukunena zoona?”"
  36,49,"“Palibe chimene akuyembekeza, koma ndi mkuwe umodzi womwe udzawamaliza mwadzidzidzi uku iwo akukangana"
  36,50,"“Ndipo sangathe kuuza wina mawu pa chinthu, ndiponso sangathe kubwerera ku maanja awo"
  36,51,“Ndipo lipenga lidzaimbidwa (loukitsa akufa); iwo adzangozindikira akutuluka m’manda kunka kwa Mbuye wawo uku akuthamanga
  36,52,"“Adzati: “Kalanga ife! Kodi ndani watidzutsa pogona pathu?” (Adzawauza): “Izi ndi zimene adalonjeza (Allah), Wachifundo chambiri ndi zimene adanena atumiki moona.”"
  36,53,“Sipadzakhala (china) koma mkuwe umodzi basi; adzangozindikira iwo onse atabweretsedwa patsogolo Pathu
  36,54,““Ndipo mzimu uliwonse lero suponderezedwa pa chilichonse. Ndipo mulipidwa pa zokhazo munkachita.”
  36,55,“Ndithu anthu aku Jannah (Munda wamtendere) lero akhala wotanganidwa ndi chisangalalo
  36,56,“Iwo ndi akazi awo ali m’mithunzi uku atatsamira mipando (ya mtengo wapamwamba)
  36,57,“M’menemo apeza (mtundu uliwonse) wa zipatso ndiponso apeza chilichonse chimene akuchifuna
  36,58,"““Mtendere (pa iwo)!” Limeneli ndi liwu lochokera kwa Mbuye (wawo), Wachisoni chosatha"
  36,59,"“Ndipo dzipatuleni lero, inu oipa"
  36,60,"“Kodi sindidakulangizeni, E inu ana a Adam kuti musapembedze satana? Ndithu, iye ndi mdani woonekera kwa inu"
  36,61,“Ndikuti ndipembedzeni Ine? Imeneyi ndi njira yolunjika
  36,62,“Ndithu (satana) adasokeretsa anthu ambiri mwa inu. Kodi simumaganizira mwanzeru
  36,63,“Iyi ndi Jahena yomwe mumalonjezedwa
  36,64,"“Iloweni lero, chifukwa cha kunkana kwanu (Allah)"
  36,65,“Lero titseka kukamwa kwawo. Ndipo manja awo atiyankhula ndipo miyendo yawo ichitira umboni pa zomwe amachita
  36,66,"“Ndipo tikadafuna, tikadafafaniza maso awo; ndipo akadakhala akuthamangira njira; koma akadapenya chotani"
  36,67,"“Ndipo tikadafuna, tikadawasintha kukhala ndi maonekedwe a nyama pamalo pawo pomwepo (pamene adali), kotero kuti sakadatha kuyenda (kunka patsogolo) ngakhale kubwerera pambuyo"
  36,68,"“Ndipo amene tikumtalikitsira moyo wake, timam’bwezeranso pambuyo m’kalengedwe kake (ndi kukhala ngati mwana). Kodi bwanji saganizira mwanzeru"
  36,69,"“Ndipo sitidamphunzitse (Mtumiki {s.a.w}) ndakatulo, ndipo nkosayenera kwa iye (kukhala mlakatuli). Qur’an sichina, koma ndichikumbutso ndi buku lomwe likulongosola chilichonse"
  36,70,"“Kuti liwachenjeze amene ali moyo, ndi kuti litsimikizike liwu (la chilango) pa osakhulupirira"
  36,71,"“Kodi saona kuti Ife tawalengera nyama, m’zimene manja Athu akonza, zomwe iwo akuti nzawo"
  36,72,“Ndi kuti tazichita kukhala zowatumikira? Zina mwa izo amazikwerapo; ndipo zina mwa izo amazidya
  36,73,“Ndipo m’menemo (m’nyama) muli zowathandiza (zambiri) ndiponso zakumwa. Nanga bwanji sathokoza
  36,74,“Ndipo adzipangira milungu (yabodza) kusiya Allah kuti athandizidwe nayo
  36,75,“(Koma) siingathe kuwathandiza; ndipo iwo (kwa milunguyo) ndi asilikali amene akonzedwa kulondera (mafanowo ndi kuwatumikira)
  36,76,“Mawu awo (onyoza Allah ndi okutsutsa iwe) asakudandaulitse. Ndithu Ife tikudziwa zimene akubisa ndi zimene akuzionetsera poyera
  36,77,“Kodi munthu sazindikira kuti Ife tidamulenga ndi dontho la umuna? Koma iye wakhala wotsutsa woonekera
  36,78,"“Ndipo akutiponyera fanizo (lotsutsa kukhoza Kwathu kuukitsa akufa) ndi kuiwala chilengedwe chake (chochokera kumadzi opanda pake). Akunena: “Ndani angaukitse mafupa pomwe ali ofumbwa?”"
  36,79,"“Nena: “Adzawaukitsa Yemwe adawalenga panthawi yoyamba. Ndipo Iye Ngodziwa kalengedwe ka mtundu uliwonse"
  36,80,“Yemwe adakupangirani moto kuchokera mu mtengo wauwisi; kenako inu mumakoleza moto m’menemo
  36,81,"“Kodi Yemwe adalenga thambo ndi nthaka (mukuganiza kuti) siwokhoza kuwalenga (iwo kachiwiri) monga momwe alili? Inde! Iye ndi Mlengi Wamkulu, Wodziwa kwambiri"
  36,82,"“Ndithu machitidwe Ake akafuna kuti chinthu chichitike, amangonena kwa icho: “Chitika!” Ndipo chimachitika (nthawi yomweyo)"
  36,83,“Kotero alemekezeke Yemwe m’manja Mwake muli ulamuliro pa chinthu chilichonse; ndipo kwa Iye (ndiko) mudzabweerera nonse